    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a fantastic car. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014it still runs like a dream! It's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable, great-looking daily driver that won't let you down, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. This example presents well with a reinforced rear subframe and recent VANOS system servicing, ensuring the high-pressure variable valve timing remains precise. The chassis maintains its composure with refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative steering rack feedback these cars are celebrated for. A mechanically sorted specimen ready for the apex.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
