      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been serviced and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014critical for this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry, offering sharp turn-in and balanced handling characteristics. Mechanically robust and performance-ready, this M3 provides a raw, analog driving experience that modern cars cannot replicate.",
